BookBot is a conversational AI chatbot built using IBM Watson Assistant that helps users get personalized book recommendations based on their genre preference, mood, or favorite author.

This project was created as part of a summer training program and aims to showcase how artificial intelligence can enhance the user experience in the world of reading and recommendations.

