ğŸš€ How It Works
The user opens the chatbot-enabled website.

BookBot starts the conversation and asks the user what they're looking for (e.g., a book for a certain mood).

Based on the responses, it uses trained intents and entities to recommend a relevant book.

The bot can loop back and provide more suggestions or end the conversation politely.

